[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "Key Middlegame Themes & Plans"]
[Black "The rupture with ...b5 (Example)"]
[Result "*"]
[FEN "r2qnrk1/pp1bbppp/n2p4/2pPp3/2P1P3/P1N3P1/1P2NPBP/R1BQ1RK1 b - - 0 1"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ Black wants to break through with ...b5. } 1... Nec7
{ First, he brings his knight to c7. } 2. f4 Bf6
{ The bishop will be powerful if the h8-a1 diagonal opens. } 3. Rb1 b5
{ Time to break through! } 4. cxb5 Nxb5 5. Nxb5 Bxb5
{ With a good game for Black.  Baragar, Fletcher   (2320)   - Seirawan, Yasser   (2600)  , 0-1, 1987. }
